title: PSP NINTENDO EMULATOR WITH COMPLETE (U) [!] ROMSET
description:
NESTERJ is a NES emulator for PSP with CFW
to install put folder in PSP/GAME on MS
To access nerterJ menu it's L-TRIGGER

THIS IS A COMPLETE NES USA ROM SET plus extras

I manually extracted ALL of the (U) [!] NES roms from
Nintendo Entertainment System (GoodNES v3.10)
then manually rezipped them with WinRar at BEST compression

Along with the complete USA set I decided to include many unlicensed
roms and alot of english translations from jap roms
since nes files are so small.

I hope everyone enjoys this work and thinks this is an awesome nes romset.

Have fun and leave good comments or post good experiences. thanks
